# Example local development variables
# Copy this file to .dev.vars and adjust as needed
#
# NOTE: the only secret the Worker reads is API_KEY. Earlier versions of this
# file mentioned WEBHOOK_SECRET — that value is not used by the Worker (there
# is no webhook endpoint). See SETUP.md for the authoritative list.

# Optional Bearer token protecting all endpoints (local dev)
# API_KEY=your_local_api_key
